Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.30,0:00:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}与朋友一起留下的记忆会在一周后被重置
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.01,0:00:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一开始听到的时候 怎么样都无法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.94,0:00:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.95,0:00:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫同学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.39,0:00:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有…有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.47,0:00:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好不容易变得那么要好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.52,0:00:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}难道就这样结束了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.48,0:00:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}决不允许发生那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.45,0:00:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}既然如此就再一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.97,0:00:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不… 踏过无数次的起点都行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.71,0:00:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}用那一成不变的话语
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.76,0:00:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请跟我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.54,0:00:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}做朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.26,0:00:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你…你突然说些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.47,0:00:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么了吗 长谷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.13,0:00:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}跟藤宫同学怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.00,0:02:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\fn腾祥铚谦钢笔简\blur0\bord0\c&H353639&}＃２ 「如何与朋友一起度过。」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.88,0:02:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你要消沉到几时啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.05,0:02:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}午休马上就要结束了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.06,0:02:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}已经不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.43,0:02:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}完全被讨厌了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.31,0:02:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘛 倒是不否定啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.39,0:02:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}倒是给我否定一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.77,0:02:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为一般来讲没人会特意跑去低头求人家跟自己做朋友的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.32,0:02:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}换作是我的话一定拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.40,0:02:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且以后也不会再接近他了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.99,0:03:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可上周就算是这样我们还是当上朋友了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.11,0:03:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那你就再加油一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.58,0:03:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我能说的就只有这些了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.62,0:03:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将吾真的很冷淡耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.00,0:03:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫香织其实并不是大家所想的 那种冷漠的人对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.21,0:03:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}相信上周的你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.01,0:03:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将吾…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.72,0:03:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我去去就回
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.43,0:03:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一二 二二 三二 四二…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.53,0:03:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.07,0:03:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.40,0:03:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天晚上吃火锅好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.16,0:03:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是爸爸点的菜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.74,0:03:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不错啊 虽然感觉现在不是吃火锅的季节
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.49,0:03:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我说啊 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.59,0:03:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.96,0:04:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}上周我有说了什么关于学校的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.47,0:04:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么也没说过喔 怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.18,0:04:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我想不起来午休是怎么度过的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.64,0:04:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}上周的每一天？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.69,0:04:15.98,PIN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}星期二
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.03,0:04:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.49,0:04:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.90,0:04:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我还可以在这里吃午饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.96,0:04:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}昨天抱歉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.46,0:04:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明明说好在教室不跟你说话的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.59,0:04:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}跟谁说的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.80,0:04:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是藤宫同学跟我说的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.71,0:04:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}「虽然可以在这里一起吃午餐 但希望你能做到这点」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.84,0:04:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那我们上周一直在这里吃午饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.31,0:04:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}难以置信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.14,0:04:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也难怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.02,0:04:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}毕竟没有记忆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.94,0:04:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}关于亲近之人的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.15,0:05:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}过了一周就会消失 被重置呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.86,0:05:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为什么你会知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.49,0:05:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}上周藤宫同学告诉我的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.37,0:05:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我连这些事都跟你说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.91,0:05:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 不过你也说过所以不要再跟你搭话了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.80,0:05:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}即使如此你还是跟我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.10,0:05:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.10,0:05:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么嘛 原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.69,0:05:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.07,0:05:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你相信我说的话了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.86,0:05:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 我的确没有上周中午的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.08,0:00:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.74,0:05:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}换了班级之后怎么说也应该见过面了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.62,0:05:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}却完全不记得你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.41,0:05:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我想这也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.96,0:06:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你对于上周的我来说是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.25,0:06:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.05,0:06:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.09,0:06:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那以后也可以一起吃午饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.01,0:06:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.26,0:06:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个 我是藤宫香织 请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.68,0:06:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 有点奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.27,0:06:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 没有这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.65,0:06:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我是长谷祐树 请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.03,0:06:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 对了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.90,0:06:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.75,0:06:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.80,0:06:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}打得很认真啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.34,0:06:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为对手是排球部的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.01,0:06:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然还是会不安啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.22,0:06:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}毕竟不记得了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.52,0:06:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.27,0:06:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没有什么好办法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.60,0:07:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.19,0:07:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.35,0:07:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}得分了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.98,0:07:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.82,0:07:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}长谷！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.61,0:07:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}完蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.70,0:07:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}长谷 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.03,0:07:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.95,0:07:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好像是长谷同学用脸去接球了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.45,0:07:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好痛的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.04,0:07:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.42,0:07:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刚才的算一分
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.42,0:07:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}别忘了记下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.26,0:07:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.97,0:07:33.47,PIN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}星期三
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.51,0:07:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}日记？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.68,0:07:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对对 把那天的心情还有做过的事情记录下来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.68,0:07:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}之后再读怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.31,0:07:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这样说不定也就能恢复记忆了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.86,0:07:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是能顺利吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.44,0:07:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且我之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.36,0:07:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.11,0:07:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}总之先写来试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.91,0:07:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}比什么都不做要好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.99,0:08:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啊 那我写写看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.00,0:08:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个 笔…笔…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.08,0:08:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在就写？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.08,0:08:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}趁着没忘赶紧记下来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.42,0:08:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和朋友长谷同学一起吃了午饭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.51,0:08:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}长谷同学吃的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.09,0:08:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是什么面包呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.72,0:08:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这个？ 这个是鸡蛋色拉面包
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.60,0:08:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}鸡蛋色拉面包？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.60,0:08:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小卖部最受欢迎的面包
